definitions.definition: Inconceivable or unimaginable ; extremely improbable in a way that goes against common sense .
examples: Nothing is unthinkable , nothing impossible to the balanced person, provided it comes out of the needs of life and is dedicated to life's further development - Lewis Mumford

definitions.definition: Extremely improper ; extremely at odds with norms of expected behavior ; taboo .
